Name: Keeping Up With the Kardashians
Title: The Kardashian Chainsaw Massacre
Desc: Kim attempts to feed the family placenta. Rob shocks everyone with new art. Bruce gets offended.
LongDescription: Kim plans to get back at her judgmental family by secretly attempting to feed them placenta; Rob shocks everyone when he takes up chainsaw art in Khloé's backyard; Jimmy Fallon's jokes get under Bruce's skin.
